> тЪая╕П **Important:** Every time you edit `Code.gs`, you must create a **new deployment version** to apply changes:
> Deploy тЖТ Manage deployments тЖТ click тЬПя╕П edit on your deployment тЖТ Version: "New version" тЖТ Deploy.

